---
import SectionTitle from "@/components/common/SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="relative w-full py-12 px-5 md:px-32 overflow-hidden">
  <SectionTitle title="자기소개" subtitle="저를 소개합니다" />

  <div
    class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-8 md:gap-[114px]"
  >
    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
      <div
        class="w-[200px] h-[275px] md:w-[302px] md:h-[415px] rounded-[15px] overflow-hidden border border-white/10"
      >
        <img
          src="/images/profile/me.webp"
          alt="정우진 프로필"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-white text-base md:text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-center md:text-left"
        >
          안녕하세요👋<br />
          저는 문제를 발견하고, 해결책을 제품으로 구현하는 과정을 즐기는 개발자 정우진입니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4 md:mt-[20px]">
        <p
          class="text-white text-base md:text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-center md:text-left"
        >
          <span class="text-[#EAB736] font-semibold"
            >기술의 온기로 더 나은 세상을 설계한다</span
          >는 신념 아래,<br />
          사람을 이해하는 기술, 그리고 사회에 긍정적인 임팩트를 남기는 서비스를 만드는
          Startup Founder로 성장하고자 노력하고 있습니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="mt-8 md:mt-[60px] grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 md:gap-x-[40px] gap-y-4 md:gap-y-[25px] w-full md:w-fit"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5 md:gap-1 items-center md:items-start">
          <span class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">17+</span>
          <span class="text-[#575757] text-sm md:text-xl font-semibold"
            >완성된 프로젝트</span
          >
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5 md:gap-1 items-center md:items-start">
          <span class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">19+</span>
          <span class="text-[#575757] text-sm md:text-xl font-semibold"
            >다루는 기술스택</span
          >
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5 md:gap-1 items-center md:items-start">
          <span class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">1</span>
          <span class="text-[#575757] text-sm md:text-xl font-semibold"
            >수상경력</span
          >
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5 md:gap-1 items-center md:items-start">
          <span class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">1720+</span
          >
          <span class="text-[#575757] text-sm md:text-xl font-semibold"
            >GitHub 기여도 (1년)</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
